{"tid":299431,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"東京飲食男旅","createTime":"2017-06-27T05:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T06:12:18.000Z","uid":90166,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d9cb3037cfa8a3ef580bff05d572cacfda4bc481","tid":299431,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:47:56.000Z","msg":"1月既時候去左東京<br />\n搭左班5:00am到羽田既hkexpress<br />\n<br />\n揀班咁既機，我個目的係去壽司大排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者有d人會覺得排咁耐隊好on9唔值<br />\n但個人興趣，其他人唔會明白～<br />\n至少我排完2粒鐘，出返黎覺得冇後悔～<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/134348_2602b4855a4d6cf7502c702207e8286f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F134348_2602b4855a4d6cf7502c702207e8286f.jpg&h=dc3b92ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/134351_891ea77a591333ee9f134d3916e30133.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F134351_891ea77a591333ee9f134d3916e30133.jpg&h=baf137f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/134353_9ab9e5f63bf95bb959cb8614274f594e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F134353_9ab9e5f63bf95bb959cb8614274f594e.jpg&h=2eb217c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後再去左築地附近間立食拉麵。排隊時我睇住師傅煮面，我都了解呢碗麵應該都唔會好好食～<br />\n但我都想試～<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/134712_a289eb32ac4c929a37f7414299604230.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F134712_a289eb32ac4c929a37f7414299604230.jpg&h=877bfd29&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/134713_a4438427b69091fbb60c15793142d190.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F134713_a4438427b69091fbb60c15793142d190.jpg&h=74e3e9da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有興趣再講lol"},{"pid":"1cf46dee4686e5a2a354720f8949e1b2b55654b4","tid":299431,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:48:51.000Z","msg":"錯區，本來想貼旅遊台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58816137838fb8cd9d4d484cb27332e3ab65618","tid":299431,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T06:09:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錯區，本來想貼旅遊台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇錯到，有得食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e092116377648d5ef180719241045ef99e3f61","tid":299431,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T06:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}